public class LevelOneTwo extends LevelParent
class extending levelparent.java. second stage level. spawns enemyplanetwo.java. level pass requirement is 30 kills.

    • checkIfGameOver

      protected void checkIfGameOver()
      checks whether the game is over (pass requirement achieved or player health drops to 0) every update. attached is a variable to ensure losegame() or gotonextlevel() function can only be called once. once the level pass requirement is met, calls a function to go to next level, passing the levelname of the next level.
